<function>

access:   public

name: inKeys

param: mixed, $value

param: array, $array

param: bool, $blank, false

return: bool

</function>

Validate that the value is a key in the list of allowed options.

* Parameters:

 * mixed //$value//: The value to validate.

 * array //$array//: An array of allowed options.

 * bool //$blank//: Allow blank values to be valid.

* Returns bool: True if valid, false if not.

Validate that the value is a key in the list of allowed options.

Given the keys of the array (second parameter), the value
(first parameter) must match at least one of those keys.